item.title: Tokay Gecko
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: We have some beautifully-colored Tokay geckos for sale. These are eating machines, and perhaps one of the most popular lizards in the world. They can even make noise. When you buy a Tokay gecko from us, you automatically receive our 100% live arrival guarantee.

item.title: Veiled Chameleon
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: We have some gorgeous captive bred Veiled chameleons for sale, produced right here at our facility. These classic reptiles originally hail from Yemen and are popular for a reason. They generally reach lengths of 14" to 18", are voracious feeders, and generally do very well in captivity. When you buy a Veiled chameleon from us, you automatically receive our 100% live arrival guarantee
